Comment: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:39.85,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,大切な落とし物を
Comment: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:42.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,知らない君が拾って
Comment: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:45.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,届けてくれたみたいな
Comment: 0,0:00:45.32,0:00:48.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,思いがけない朝
Comment: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:51.20,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,そういえば大事なものは
Comment: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:53.95,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,ちゃんと名前を書かなくじゃ
Comment: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:56.95,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,どこかで失くしてしまうと
Comment: 0,0:00:56.95,0:00:59.83,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,よく言われてたのに
Comment: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:02.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,誰かの　せいじゃなくて
Comment: 0,0:01:02.63,0:01:05.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,誰かの　ものでもなくて
Comment: 0,0:01:05.38,0:01:08.17,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,変わらず　世界は
Comment: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:10.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,そこにあるよ
Comment: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:13.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,風と　さあ手と手繋いで
Comment: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:16.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,空と　息を合わせて
Comment: 0,0:01:16.31,0:01:18.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,行こう　動き出した
Comment: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:22.19,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,心の矢印
Comment: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:24.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,君と　そう君とならば
Comment: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:28.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,ならば　そう君とだから
Comment: 0,0:01:28.36,0:01:36.37,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,何が起きるかなんかわからない未来が
Comment: 0,0:01:36.37,0:01:38.24,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,走る
Comment: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:42.87,OPJP,last,0,0,0,karaoke,キラキラ　跳ねてる
Comment: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:55.05,OPJP,,0,0,0,,OPJP End
Comment: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:25.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,OPCN Start
Comment: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:39.85,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,我那珍貴的失物
Comment: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:42.52,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,被素不相識的你撿起
Comment: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:45.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,把它交還給我
Comment: 0,0:00:45.32,0:00:48.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,出乎意料的清晨
Comment: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:51.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,這麼說來　重要的東西
Comment: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:53.95,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,一定要寫上名字
Comment: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:56.95,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,不然會丟失於不知何處
Comment: 0,0:00:56.95,0:00:59.83,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,經常被這樣告誡
Comment: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:02.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,不是任何人的錯
Comment: 0,0:01:02.63,0:01:05.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,也不屬於任何人
Comment: 0,0:01:05.38,0:01:08.17,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,一成不變的世界
Comment: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:10.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,存在於此
Comment: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:13.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,隨風　來吧手牽手
Comment: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:16.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,於空　配合對方步調
Comment: 0,0:01:16.31,0:01:18.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,走吧　出發了
Comment: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:22.19,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,心之所向
Comment: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:24.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,與你　沒錯　如果與你一起
Comment: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:28.36,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒錯　正因為與你一起
Comment: 0,0:01:28.36,0:01:36.37,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,向著未知的未來
Comment: 0,0:01:36.37,0:01:38.24,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,奔跑
Comment: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:42.87,OPCN,last,0,0,0,karaoke,閃耀奪目
Comment: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:55.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,OPCN End
Comment: 0,0:21:42.49,0:21:42.53,EDJP,,0,0,0,,EDJP Start
Comment: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:52.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,葉っぱがささやく　真夜中
Comment: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:58.61,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,ふわり　心地よくて
Comment: 0,0:21:58.61,0:22:04.52,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,まだ　話したりないけど
Comment: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:11.27,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,はぁ　あくびが出るよ
Comment: 0,0:22:11.27,0:22:17.29,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,明日は晴れるかな
Comment: 0,0:22:17.29,0:22:27.45,EDJP,long,0,0,0,karaoke,ちぐはぐ　おまじない　かけるよ
Comment: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:34.17,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,空　泳ぐ　綿あめ
Comment: 0,0:22:34.17,0:22:39.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,お味はいかが
Comment: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:46.64,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,シャボン玉　ぷかぷか
Comment: 0,0:22:46.64,0:22:52.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,向こう岸までどうぞ
Comment: 0,0:22:52.70,0:23:00.73,EDJP,long,0,0,0,karaoke,ありゃりゃ　全部　だったの
Comment: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:11.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,星たちが　ほら　笑ってる
Comment: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:12.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,,EDJP End
Comment: 0,0:21:42.49,0:21:42.53,EDCN,,0,0,0,,EDCN Start
Comment: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:52.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,樹葉輕語　夜深人靜
Comment: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:58.61,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,清風吹拂　心曠神怡
Comment: 0,0:21:58.61,0:22:04.52,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,還有千言萬語未能出口
Comment: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:11.27,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,就不經意打了個哈欠
Comment: 0,0:22:11.27,0:22:17.29,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,明天會放晴嗎
Comment: 0,0:22:17.29,0:22:27.45,EDCN,long,0,0,0,karaoke,一起來念生疏的咒語
Comment: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:34.17,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,空中飄舞的棉花糖
Comment: 0,0:22:34.17,0:22:39.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,要不要嚐嚐呢
Comment: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:46.64,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,泡泡紛紛揚揚
Comment: 0,0:22:46.64,0:22:52.70,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,歡迎前往對岸
Comment: 0,0:22:52.70,0:23:00.73,EDCN,long,0,0,0,karaoke,哎呀　這是夢境一場嗎
Comment: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:11.33,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,看　繁星正對我們微笑
